    <string name="title_text">This quiz contains a few questions which may be related to different
        topics such as mathematics, astronomy, or chemistry.
        \n
        \nWhen you press the Start button, the
        quiz and timer will start. Once you are done with the quiz, press the Done button.
        The timer stops once you press the Done button and your score and the time taken will be
        displayed at the bottom of the screen.
        \n
        \nThe app keeps a list of ten of the highest scores,
        and if your score is high enough, it will be added to the list upon pressing the Done
        button.</string>
